    <headline>Frequent lightning ongoing, yellow level, Western Norway south of Stad, 2022-07-20T05:15:00+00:00, 2022-07-20T16:00:00+00:00</headline>
    <description>Scattered thunderstorms have been observed with frequent lightning over Western Norway. The thunderstorm is expected to continue until tonight. There are large local differences in intensity. Some places will not experience any thunderstorms</description>
    <instruction>Stay up to date on the development of the weather and the weather forecast. Monitor the weather radar or lyn.met.no. Disconnect electrical appliances. Adjust driving speed according to the road/weather conditions. Seek shelter. Avoid open plains and large trees. Do not swim or bathe. </instruction>
